title: Student Statistics from the Landesdatenbank NRW (Table Series 21311)
text: downloaded raw data included package, size roughly 200 MB. licence requires list changes part source notes (see ). data transformation steps performed: Column names transformed using janitor::clean_names(). Technical columns ending “QUAL”, “ERR”, “LOCK” removed. original data uses value labels separate lookup tables. R package, labels transformed factors using description lookup tables.

what: License for the data from the Landesdatenbank NRW / Destatis
title: Student Statistics from the Landesdatenbank NRW (Table Series 21311)
text: data package obtained Landesdatenbank NRW using code “21311” “Statistik der Studenten”. licence data obtained Landesdatenbank NRW / Destatis available (see paragraph 2 section 2): Data licence Germany – attribution – Version 2.0. Paragraph 2 section 3 requires including reference dataset (URI) available. best knowledge, Landesdatenbank NRW yet provide Uniform Resource Identifiers (URI) identify tables. Paragraph 3 stipulates “changes, editing, new designs amendments must marked source note”. Compared raw data, following changes made: (1) column names changed lower case, (2) technical columns excluded (3) value labels turned factors using description value label. code transformations available package.
